title: This week on RELEASED | ROSÉ (Official Trailer)
author: BLACKPINK
description: Join ROSÉ this week on RELEASED as she tests how well her friends know her, see what artists are on her playlist, and performs solos with various instruments. All this leading up to the world premiere of her new music video “On The Ground”! Can't miss Music moments. RELEASED, every Thursday, only on YouTube. #RELEASEDonYT #ROSÉ  #OnTheGround

localize.description: 加入ROSÉ本周的RELEASED，她将测试她的朋友们对她的了解程度，看看她的播放列表上有哪些艺术家，并用各种乐器进行独奏。所有这些都将在她的新音乐录影带 "On The Ground "的全球首映之前完成。不容错过的音乐时刻。RELEASED，每周四，只在YouTube上播放。#＃RELEASEDonYT＃ROSÉ＃OnTheGround。
localize.title: 本周《RELEASED》｜ROSÉ (官方预告片)
